com.apriori.di

Annotation Type OptionalQualifier


  • @Target(value=ANNOTATION_TYPE)
 @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
 @Documented
public @interface OptionalQualifier
    An annotation that represents an optional qualifier. This is like Qualifier except that it indicates that it is not an error if no explicit binding is provided for the qualifier. In such a case, a binding will be used that does not contain the qualifier in the key.
